main event: A civilian observed a strange object with red, white, and green lights for about 24 minutes in Sanford, Florida on November 18, 1966.
interesting points: The object was described as having an unusual shape consistent with a helicopter,The observer was located approximately four miles south of Sanford,The observation was made at night under partly cloudy conditions,There were no other aircraft reported in the area at the time of the sighting,The sighting ended when the object disappeared over the horizon.
sighted object: a strange shaped object with red, white, and green lights
witness description: Miss Mary K. Ferre, 21 years old, secretary at an insurance firm, appeared honest about the report.
